metadata.description: Shellz Orb is a lore and art-based brand. Our journey begins in NFTs with the goal of making Web3 within an arm's reach of every person on earth. There are 9,000 Shellz wandering in a post-apocalyptic world, each one is a ticket into The Orb. Hand drawn by a team of 8 artists led by Voyager, whose work has been seen in Magic the Gathering, League of Legends, and more.
